Q.Consider first n even numbers starting from zero(0).Complete the code segment to calculate sum of all these numbers divisible by 3 .
  Print the sum.
  
  
  program code:-
  
  import java.util.Scanner;
  public class Exercise1_3 {
       public static void main(String[] args) {
	   Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
	   int n=sc.nextInt();
	   int sum=0;
     
       for(int i=0;i<2*n;i+=2)
       {
         if(i%3==0)
           
           sum+=i;
       }
        
        System.out.print(sum);
        }
   }
